                HOW-TO

This webhook uses Bing image search for finding bewbs and posting them to Slack,
triggered GitHub commits (or really any POST request).

How do you like your boobs?
---------------------------

Customize results by altering the webhook URL.

http://slacker.fart.attorney

Optional parameters:

  hook  Webhook URL provided by Slack
        REQUIRED.

  q     Query to search for images
        Default: best cleavage ever

  bot   Bot name in Slack
        Default: push bot

  chan  Channel in Slack to post to
        Default: mobile

  msg   Message to display along with pic
        Default: #titsforcommits

Add GitHub hook
---------------

1. Go to repo
2. Go to Settings
3. Go to Webhooks & Services
4. Click Add webhook
5. Enter the url you previously constructed in Payload URL
6. Click Add webhook


